cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.IR 

This paper is about named entity recognition using neural architectures. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with natural language processing and computational linguistics. The paper also uses machine learning techniques, so cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another likely category. Additionally, the paper uses unsupervised learning, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also deals with information retrieval, which is covered under cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is another possible category, as the paper uses neural networks.
